Tic Tac Toe (Player vs AI)
LIVE WEBISTE LINK
https://ai-problemsolving-ra2411026050103-1.onrender.com

A simple web-based Tic Tac Toe game built using Flask, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, where the player competes against an AI opponent.

🚀 Features
👤 Player vs Computer mode
🤖 AI opponent with smart move logic
🎨 Modern and clean UI design
⚡ Fast and lightweight gameplay
🔁 Restart game option
📱 Responsive design for mobile and desktop
🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Backend: Python (Flask)
Deployment: Render
📁 Project Structure
app.py
templates/index.html
static/style.css
static/script.js
⚙️ How to Run Locally
Install Flask:
pip install flask
Run the app:
python app.py

🤖 AI Logic
Checks for winning move
Blocks player’s winning move
Takes center if available
Otherwise selects a random move
🌐 Deployment

Deployed using Render with:

Start command: gunicorn app:app
📌 Future Improvements
Minimax unbeatable AI
Score tracking system
Sound effects
Better mobile UI
👨‍💻 Author

